snippet.title: Plotkin deposition
snippet.description:
This is the first and only time a vaccine developer/promoter has ever been put under oath and must tell the truth.  Big difference between what they say under oath and what they tell the public.  Watching this video is an important part of our education as free, informed citizens of a representative democracy - and what happens when we give unaccountable experts too much power.

We have a downloadable MP3 and written transcript here: https://censored.vaxcalc.org/2019/06/21/only-time-a-vaccine-inventor-promoter-has-been-put-under-oath/
